  <brief_title>An Open-Label Study of the Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Repeated-Dose Micafungin in Neonates</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Open-Label Study of the Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Repeated-Dose Micafungin in Neonates</official_title>
