  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate pharmacokinetics and safety of intravenous micafungin in neonates
      with suspected candida infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Subjects will be stratified by weight to receive one of two doses of study drug
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
